n></span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: center; line-height: 28.5pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family:??;color:black;font-size: 22pt; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ??; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">广州市旅游局关于征求《</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size: 22pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">广州市旅行社组织</span></span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: center; line-height: 28.5pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size: 22pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">接待游客来穗旅游奖励办法</span><span style=\"font-family:??;color:black;font-size: 22pt; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ??; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">（修订</span></span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: center; line-height: 28.5pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly;\"><span style=\"font-family:??;color:black;font-size: 22pt; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ??; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">征求意见稿）》的意见的通知</span></span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; line-height: 28.5pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-line-height-rule: exactly;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: ??;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;\">　　</span></span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; line-height: 28.5pt; text-indent: 32pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-cha