宋体;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: center; line-height: 28.5pt; vertical-align: baseline; mso-line-height-rule: exactly;\"><span style=\"font-size: 22pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 18.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">广州市旅游局关于批准设立</span></span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: center; line-height: 28.5pt; vertical-align: baseline; mso-line-height-rule: exactly;\"><span style=\"font-size: 22pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 18.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">广州亚太国际旅行社有限公司的批<span style=\"mso-font-width: 85%;\">复</span></span></span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.5pt; vertical-align: baseline; mso-line-height-rule: exactly;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.5pt; vertical-align: baseline; mso-line-height-rule: exactly;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">蓝丽琼：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\"> </span></span></span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.5pt; text-indent: 31.7pt; vertical-align: baseline; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 1.98;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">您提交的设立旅行社申请材料收悉。</span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">经审核，您和梁毅投资的</span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">广州亚太国际旅行社有限公司</span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">符合</span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">《中华人民共和国旅游法》、《旅行社条例》及《旅行社条例实施细则》规定的条件，我局批准设立。现将有关事项核定如下：</span></span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.5pt; text-indent: 31.35pt; vertical-align: baseline; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96;\"><span style=\"font-family: 黑体; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">一、旅行社名称：</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;\">广州亚太国际旅行社有限公司</span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.5pt; text-indent: 31.35pt; vertical-align: baseline; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96;\"><span style=\"font-family: 黑体; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">二、英文名称：</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \'仿宋_GB2312\',\'serif\';\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">GUANGZHOU ASIA-PACIFIC INTERNATIONALTRAVEL SERVICE</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\"> CO.,LTD</span></span></span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.5pt; text-indent: 31.35pt; vertical-align: baseline; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96;\"><span style=\"font-family: 黑体; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">三、许可经营业务：</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;\">境内旅游与入境旅游</span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.5pt; text-indent: 31.35pt; vertical-align: baseline; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96;\"><span style=\"font-family: 黑体; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">四、出资人、出资额及其出资比例：</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">出资总额</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">30</span></span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">万元人民币。其中，蓝丽琼出资</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">27</span></span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">万元，占</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">90%</span></span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">；梁毅出资</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">3</span></span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">万元，占</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">10%</span></span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">。</span></span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.5pt; text-indent: 31.35pt; vertical-align: baseline; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96;\"><span style=\"font-family: 黑体; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">五、法定代表人</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;\">：蓝丽琼</span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.5pt; text-indent: 31.35pt; vertical-align: baseline; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96;\"><span style=\"font-family: 黑体; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">六、企业形式：</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;\">有限责任公司</span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.5pt; text-indent: 31.35pt; vertical-align: baseline; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96;\"><span style=\"font-family: 黑体; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">七、经营场所：</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">广州市天河区先烈东路</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">190</span></span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">号</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">1104</span></span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">房</span></span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.5pt; text-indent: 31.35pt; vertical-align: baseline; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96;\"><span style=\"font-family: 黑体; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">八、许可证编号：</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \'仿宋_GB2312\',\'serif\'; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;\">L-GD01994 </span></span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.5pt; text-indent: 31.35pt; vertical-align: baseline; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">请持该批准文件及旅行社业务经营许可证（副本）在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">1</span></span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">个月内办妥税务登记、组织机构代码证及公章备案。</span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">根据《中华人民共和国旅游法》第三十一条、《旅行社条例》第十三条，</span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">广州亚太国际旅行社有限公司</span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">应当在办妥上述事项后</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">3</span></span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">个工作日内，</span><span style=\"color: black; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">在</span></span><span style=\"color: black;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">国家旅游局指定的银行</span></span><span style=\"color: black; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">开设专门的旅游服务质量保证金账户，</span></span><span style=\"color: black;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">存入</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">20</span></span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">万元旅游服务质量保证金或者办理同等额度的银行担保，并在此后</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">7</span></span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">个工作日内将相关的证明文件交回我局备案。您可以</span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">通过广州市商事主体信息公示平台（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">http://cri.gz.gov.cn</span></span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">）查询许可审批的内容。</span></span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.5pt; text-indent: 31.35pt; vertical-align: baseline; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96; tab-stops: 376.25pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;\">旅行社开业后，应当遵守《中华人民共和国旅游法》、《旅行社条例》和《旅行社条例实施细则》及其它有关法律、法规和规章，确保守法经营、优质服务。</span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.5pt; text-indent: 31.35pt; vertical-align: baseline; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">专此批复</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span></span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.5pt; text-indent: 31.35pt; vertical-align: baseline; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.5pt; text-indent: 31.35pt; vertical-align: baseline; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.5pt; text-indent: 31.35pt; vertical-align: baseline; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.5pt; text-indent: 294.25pt; vertical-align: baseline; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 18.39; tab-stops: 376.25pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;\">广州市旅游局</span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.5pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; tab-stops: 375.65pt 391.3pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">2015</span></span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">1</span></span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">28</span></span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">日</span></span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span>');
INSERT INTO DS_CMS_PAGE (ID, SITEID, CATEGORYID, STATUS, TITLE, URL, METAKEYWORDS, METADESCRIPTION, SUMMARY, RELEASETIME, RELEASESOURCE, RELEASEUSER, IMG, IMGTOP, PAGETOP, CONTENT) VALUES (1099, 5, 25, 1, '关于批准广州慧旅信息科技有限公司经营旅游业务的批复', '/a/lxsgl/1099.html', '', '', '关于批准广州慧旅信息科技有限公司经营旅游业务的批复', '2015-02-07 17:38:00', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0, '<div style=\"top: 0px;\">??</div><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p align=\"right\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: right; line-height: 26.5pt; -ms-word-break: break-all; mso-line-height-rule: exactly;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style=\"color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">穗旅发〔</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">2015</span></span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">〕</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">18</span></span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">号</span></span></span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: center; line-height: 28.5pt; vertical-align: baseline; mso-line-height-rule: exactly;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 22pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 18.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: center; line-height: 28.5pt; vertical-align: baseline; mso-line-height-rule: exactly;\"><span style=\"font-size: 22pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 18.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">广州市旅游局关于批准广州慧旅信息科技有限公司经营境内旅游和入境旅游业务的批<span style=\"mso-font-width: 85%;\">复</span></span></span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.5pt; vertical-align: baseline; mso-line-height-rule: exactly;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.5pt; vertical-align: baseline; mso-line-height-rule: exactly;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">广州慧旅信息科技有限公司：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\"> </span></span></span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.5pt; text-indent: 31.7pt; vertical-align: baseline; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 1.98;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">你公司提交的设立旅行社申请材料收悉。</span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">经审核，你公司符合</span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">《中华人民共和国旅游法》、《旅行社条例》及《旅行社条例实施细则》规定的条件，我局批准你公司经营境内旅游和入境旅游业务。现将有关事项核定如下：</span></span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.5pt; text-indent: 31.35pt; vertical-align: baseline; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96;\"><span style=\"font-family: 黑体; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">一、公司名称：</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;\">广州慧旅信息科技有限公司</span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.5pt; text-indent: 31.35pt; vertical-align: baseline; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 黑体; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\">二、英文名称：</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">GUANGZHOU</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\"> HUILV INFORMATION AND TECHNOLOGY </span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">CO.,LTD</span></span></span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.5pt; text-indent: 31.35pt; vertical-align: baseline; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96;\"><span style=\"font-family: 黑体; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">三、许可经营业务：</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;\">境内旅游与入境旅游</span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.5pt; text-indent: 31.35pt; vertical-align: baseline; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96;\"><span style=\"font-family: 黑体; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">四、出资人、出资额及其出资比例：</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">广州虫洞网络科技有限公司独资</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">30</span></span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">万元人民币，占</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">100%</span></span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">。</span></span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.5pt; text-indent: 31.35pt; vertical-align: baseline; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96;\"><span style=\"font-family: 黑体; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">五、法定代表人</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;\">：李伊</span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.5pt; text-indent: 31.35pt; vertical-align: baseline; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96;\"><span style=\"font-family: 黑体; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">六、企业形式：</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;\">有限责任公司</span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.5pt; text-indent: 31.35pt; vertical-align: baseline; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96;\"><span style=\"font-family: 黑体; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">七、经营场所：</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">广州市海珠区新港西路</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">135</span></span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">号大院中大蒲园区</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">628</span></span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">栋中大科技园</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">A</span></span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">座自编号</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">806</span></span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">807</span></span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">房</span></span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-indent: 31.7pt; mso-char-indent-count: 1.98;\"><span style=\"font-family: 黑体; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">八、许可证编号：</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;\">L-GD01996 </span></span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.5pt; text-indent: 31.35pt; vertical-align: baseline; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">请持该批准文件及旅行社业务经营许可证（副本）在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">1</span></span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">个月内办妥税务登记、组织机构代码证及公章备案。</span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">根据《中华人民共和国旅游法》第三十一条、《旅行社条例》第十三条，</span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">你公司</span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">应当在办妥上述事项后</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">3</span></span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">个工作日内，</span><span style=\"color: black; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">在</span></span><span style=\"color: black;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">国家旅游局指定的银行</span></span><span style=\"color: black; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">开设专门的旅游服务质量保证金账户，</span></span><span style=\"color: black;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">存入</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">20</span></span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">万元旅游服务质量保证金或者办理同等额度的银行担保，并在此后</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">7</span></span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">个工作日内将相关的证明文件交回我局备案。你公司可以</span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">通过广州市商事主体信息公示平台（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">http://cri.gz.gov.cn</span></span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">）查询许可审批的内容。</span></span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.5pt; text-indent: 31.35pt; vertical-align: baseline; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96; tab-stops: 376.25pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;\">你公司开业后，应当遵守《中华人民共和国旅游法》、《旅行社条例》和《旅行社条例实施细则》及其它有关法律、法规和规章，确保守法经营、优质服务。</span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.5pt; text-indent: 31.35pt; vertical-align: baseline; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">专此批复</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span></span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.5pt; text-indent: 31.35pt; vertical-align: baseline; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.5pt; text-indent: 31.35pt; vertical-align: baseline; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.5pt; text-indent: 31.35pt; vertical-align: baseline; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.5pt; text-indent: 294.25pt; vertical-align: baseline; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 18.39; tab-stops: 376.25pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;\">广州市旅游局</span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.5pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; tab-stops: 375.65pt 391.3pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">&nbsp;</span></span><st1:chsdate year=\"2015\" month=\"2\" day=\"6\" islunardate=\"False\" isrocdate=\"False\" w:st=\"on\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">2015</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">年2</span></span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">月6</span></span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">日</span></span></span></st1:chsdate></span></span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span>');
INSERT INTO DS_CMS_PAGE (ID, SITEID, CATEGORYID, STATUS, TITLE, URL, METAKEYWORDS, METADESCRIPTION, SUMMARY, RELEASETIME, RELEASESOURCE, RELEASEUSER, IMG, IMGTOP, PAGETOP, CONTENT) VALUES (1107, 5, 59, 1, '关于做好2015年度第一次全国导游人员资格考试工作的通知', '/a/tzgsgg/1107.html', '', '', '关于做好2015年度第一次全国导游人员资格考试工作的通知', '2014-12-26 17:46:33', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0, '<div style=\"top: 0px;\"></div><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><div style=\"mso-layout-grid-char-alt: -1675;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: center; line-height: 28.5pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">穗旅发〔</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">2014</span></span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">〕</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">174</span></span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">号</span></span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.5pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 22pt; font-weight: normal; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-\"><strong><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></strong></span></strong></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: center; line-height: 28.5pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 22pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\">&nbsp;</span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: center; line-height: 28.5pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><span style=\"color: black; font-size: 22pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi- mso-font-kerning: 0pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">广州市旅游局关于做好<span lang=\"EN-US\">2015</span>年度第一次</span></strong></span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: center; line-height: 28.5pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"color: black; font-size: 22pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi- mso-font-kerning: 0pt;\"><strong>全国导游人员资格考试工作的通知</strong></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 22pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt;\"> </span></span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; line-height: 28.5pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: black; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; line-height: 28.5pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><span style=\"color: black; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;\">广州地区各旅行社、导游服务管理公司、广州市旅游商务职业学校和有关旅游院校：</span></span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; line-height: 28.5pt; text-indent: 32.25pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><span style=\"color: black; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">根据广东省旅游局《广东省旅游局关于做好我省</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">2015</span></span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">年度第一次全国导游人员资格考试工作的通知》</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">(</span></span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">粤旅明电〔</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">2014</span></span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">〕</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">201</span></span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">号</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">)</span></span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">文件精神，现对广州地区</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">2015</span></span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">年度第一次全国导游人员资格考试工作通知如下：</span></span></span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; line-height: 28.5pt; text-indent: 32.25pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><span style=\"color: black; font-family: 黑体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">一、报名时间</span></span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; line-height: 28.5pt; text-indent: 32.25pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><span style=\"color: black; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">网络报名时间：</span><st1:chsdate year=\"2014\" month=\"12\" day=\"25\" islunardate=\"False\" isrocdate=\"False\" w:st=\"on\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">2014</span></span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">12</span></span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">25</span></span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">日</span></st1:chsdate><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">至</span><st1:c