0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">　　</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">2.</span></span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">加考笔试“广东导游基础知识”，每人</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">92</span></span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">元。</span></span></span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; line-height: 28.5pt; text-indent: 38.2pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.45; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: black; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">(</span></span><span style=\"color: black; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">三</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">)</span></span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">网银缴费</span></span></span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; line-height: 28.5pt; text-indent: 32.25pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><span style=\"color: black; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;\">考生须开通网银功能，并保证银行卡存款足额，登录报名账号后点击缴费，按提示完成。</span></span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; line-height: 28.5pt; text-indent: 32.25pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: black; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">(</span></span><span style=\"color: black; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">四</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">)</span></span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">银行缴费</span></span></span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; line-height: 28.5pt; text-indent: 32.25pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><span style=\"color: black; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;\">考生需要登录报名账号，点击打印《缴费通知单》，持《缴费通知单》到指定银行缴费。</span></span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; line-height: 28.5pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; tab-stops: 29.1pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><span style=\"color: black; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;\">　　</span></span><span style=\"color: black; font-family: 黑体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">六、相关事项：</span></span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; line-height: 28.5pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><span style=\"color: black; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">　　</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">(</span></span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">一</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">)</span></span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">有关报考的语种、报考条件、报名程序及必备资料、参考书、考试科目和内容、命题及考试时间、评卷和发证等，依照广东省旅游局《广东省旅游局关于做好我省</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">2015</span></span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">年度第一次全国导游人员资格考试工作的通知》</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">(</span></span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">粤旅明电〔</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">2014</span></span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">〕</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">201</span></span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">号</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">)</span></span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">文件要求执行，请各单位、各考生在广东省旅游局政务网站</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">(www.gdta.gov.cn)</span></span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">查询有关考试信息和下载有关表格。</span></span></span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; line-height: 28.5pt; text-indent: 32.25pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: black; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">(</span></span><span style=\"color: black; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">二</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">)</span></span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">各单位在具体组织实施过程中有何问题，请及时向我局</span></span></span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; line-height: 28.5pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><span style=\"color: black; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;\">行业培训指导处反映。</span></span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; line-height: 28.5pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: black; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; line-height: 28.5pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: black; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; line-height: 28.5pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: black; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; line-height: 28.5pt; text-indent: 283.3pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 18.17; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><span style=\"color: black; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;\">广州市旅游局</span></span></p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span><p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; line-height: 28.5pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; tab-stops: 378.3pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;\"><span style=\"color: black; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">　　</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nb